@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Gateway
participant VMService
participant OpenNebula

User -> Frontend: Open terminal tab
Frontend -> Gateway: WS connect /terminal
Gateway -> VMService: authorize + open stream
VMService -> OpenNebula: request console/exec channel
OpenNebula --> VMService: stream channel
VMService --> Gateway: terminal stream
Gateway --> Frontend: bidirectional stream
User -> Frontend: type command
Frontend -> Gateway: command
Gateway -> VMService: forward
VMService -> OpenNebula: execute
OpenNebula --> VMService: output
VMService --> Gateway: output
Gateway --> Frontend: render output
@enduml
